        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Victoria Chen</h3>
        <p class="text-gold-500 font-medium mb-4">Senior Partner & CIO</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Victoria oversees our investment strategy and portfolio management. Her expertise in alternative investments and risk management has helped clients navigate complex market environments.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
          <button class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300" aria-label="Social media profile" disabled>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300" aria-label="Social media profile" disabled>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Member 3 -->
      <div class="group text-center">
        <div class="relative mb-8">
          <div class="w-64 h-64 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-200 to-slate-300 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-slate-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-500/20 to-transparent rounded-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">James Montgomery</h3>
        <p class="text-gold-500 font-medium mb-4">Senior Partner & Head of Estate Planning</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          James specializes in complex estate planning and wealth transfer strategies. His expertise in tax law and family governance has helped numerous families preserve their legacies.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
          <button class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300" aria-label="Social media profile" disabled>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300" aria-label="Social media profile" disabled>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Advisory Team -->
  <Section 
    title="Advisory Team"
    subtitle="Specialized Expertise"
    description="Our advisory team brings specialized knowledge in key areas of wealth management and financial planning."
    className="bg-slate-50"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Sarah Williams</h3>
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Tax Strategy Specialist</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Expert in advanced tax planning and optimization strategies for high-net-worth individuals.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3a3 3 0 013-3h3a3 3 0 013 3v3m-6-9V6a3 3 0 013-3h3a3 3 0 013 3v3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Michael Rodriguez</h3>
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Estate Planning Attorney</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Specializes in complex trust structures and multi-generational wealth transfer strategies.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Emily Thompson</h3>
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Philanthropy Advisor</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Helps families develop and implement strategic philanthropic initiatives and charitable giving plans.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15l-1.5 18h-12L4.5 3zM9.75 9h4.5M9.75 12h4.5M9.75 15h4.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">David Kim</h3>
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">International Planning</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Expert in cross-border wealth management and international tax optimization strategies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Team Values -->
  <Section 
    title="Our Commitment"
    subtitle="What Sets Us Apart"
    description="The principles and values that guide our team in serving our clients with excellence."
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <Card 
        title="Client-First Approach"
        description="Every decision we make is guided by what's best for our clients, not what's most profitable for our firm."
        icon="target"
      />
      
      <Card 
        title="Continuous Learning"
        description="We invest heavily in ongoing education and professional development to stay at the forefront of our field."
        icon="book"
      />
      
      <Card 
        title="Collaborative Excellence"
        description="Our team works together seamlessly, leveraging each member's expertise to deliver comprehensive solutions."
        icon="handshake"
      />
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <Section 
    title="Ready to Work With Our Team?"
    description="Schedule a consultation to discuss how our experienced professionals can help achieve your wealth management objectives."
    className="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 to-slate-900 text-white"
  >
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
        <a 
          href="/wealth-management-site/contact" 
          class="group inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gold-500 text-navy-900 font-medium rounded-none hover:bg-gold-400 transition-all duration-300 ease-out transform hover:scale-105 font-sans tracking-wide"
        >
          <span>Schedule Consultation</span>
          <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
